\begin_deeper
\begin_layout Itemize
What instruments should the government use to redistribute? 
\begin_inset VSpace bigskip
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
Atkinson-Stiglitz (1976) 
\begin_inset Formula $\rightarrow$
\end_inset

 only income taxes/cash transfers.
\begin_inset VSpace bigskip
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
Akerlof (1978) 
\begin_inset Formula $\rightarrow$
\end_inset

 income taxes/cash transfers, but possibly dependent on 
\emph on
tags.
\emph default

\begin_inset VSpace bigskip
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
What about in-kind benefits? Commodity taxes/subsidies? Ordeals?
\begin_inset VSpace bigskip
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
This paper shows under what conditions to use these other instruments and
 how.
