Event Study estimates:
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
Y_{isct}=\alpha_{i}+\gamma_{st}+\sum_{\tau}D_{ct}^{\tau}+\sum\delta_{\tau}\left(Treated_{ic}\times D_{ct}^{\tau}\right)+\epsilon_{isct}
\]

\end_inset

where 
\begin_inset Formula $Y_{isct}$
\end_inset

 is outcome for ZIP 
\begin_inset Formula $i$
\end_inset

 in state 
\begin_inset Formula $s$
\end_inset

 for closure 
\begin_inset Formula $c$
\end_inset

 in quarter 
\begin_inset Formula $t$
\end_inset

; 
\begin_inset Formula $\alpha_{i}$
\end_inset

 are ZIP FEs; 
\begin_inset Formula $\gamma_{st}$
\end_inset

 are state
\begin_inset Formula $\times$
\end_inset

quarter FEs; 
\begin_inset Formula $Treated_{ic}$
\end_inset

 indicates treatment; 
\begin_inset Formula $D_{ct}^{\tau}$
\end_inset

 are indicators for observations 
\begin_inset Formula $\tau$
\end_inset

 quarters before/after the closure.
